; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the oversell path in FIFO lot matching.  When the total sale
; amount exceeds all available lot holdings, the unmatched remainder
; is split into a separate unannotated posting.

2024/01/01 Buy Lot 1
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/01/01]
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Buy Lot 2
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$160.00} [2024/02/01]
    Assets:Cash

2024/03/01 Sell More Than Holdings
    Assets:Brokerage    -15 AAPL @ $170.00
    Assets:Cash

test --lot-matching fifo reg Assets:Brokerage
24-Jan-01 Buy Lot 1             Assets:Brokerage             5 AAPL       5 AAPL
24-Feb-01 Buy Lot 2             Assets:Brokerage             5 AAPL      10 AAPL
24-Mar-01 Sell More Than Hold.. Assets:Brokerage            -5 AAPL       5 AAPL
                                Assets:Brokerage            -5 AAPL            0
                                Assets:Brokerage            -5 AAPL      -5 AAPL
end test
